{"id":233009935,"title":"好啦現在每人每週只能買兩片","content":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7d3e5cbe-ee68-4287-b2a2-5b885da1610f/1280.jpeg\n稍早朋友傳這張圖給我\n其實我本來沒什麼差的人\n反正原本就不太需要\n就給有需要人的人用吧\n那時大家都在排口罩時我是這麼想的\n\n沒想到阿爸初三半夜心肌梗塞現在還在住院中\n搞得我現在頻繁進出醫院缺無口罩可用😓\n想買還買不到\n護理師還要我想辦法買口罩來給阿爸用\n\n好啦現在一人一週買兩片\n我都不知道該怎麼辦才好了...(暈)\n\n只能說感謝那些卯起來拼命囤貨的人\n讓政府使用這樣的方法\n才讓大家都有口罩能買\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e898d1a0-6c31-4e66-88de-39c8cf1e8f80/1280.jpeg\nP.S這是初三那晚在還在急診室等待時","excerpt":"稍早朋友傳這張圖給我，其實我本來沒什麼差的人，反正原本就不太需要，就給有需要人的人用吧，那時大家都在排口罩時我是這麼想的，沒想到阿爸初三半夜心肌梗塞現在還在住院中，搞得我現在頻繁進出醫院缺無口罩可用，","anonymousSchool":true,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"75a726e6-d4e3-4902-a410-2430a39fffcb","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-02-03T14:39:10.986Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-03T14:40:25.716Z","commentCount":4,"likeCount":17,"tags":[],"topics":[],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"心情","forumAlias":"mood","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":15},{"id":"514c2569-fd53-4d9d-a415-bf0f88e7329f","count":2}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7d3e5cbe-ee68-4287-b2a2-5b885da1610f/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e898d1a0-6c31-4e66-88de-39c8cf1e8f80/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"7130c92f-3cda-4cda-ad5e-1b3e906d65d7","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7d3e5cbe-ee68-4287-b2a2-5b885da1610f/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7d3e5cbe-ee68-4287-b2a2-5b885da1610f/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7d3e5cbe-ee68-4287-b2a2-5b885da1610f/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-02-03T14:39:10.986Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-03T14:40:25.716Z","width":459,"h